<body><p><indexterm>count topics in file</indexterm><indexterm>report<indexterm>topic
count</indexterm></indexterm>Before this command can be used, you
must set up the TopicHeadings section of the <filepath>fm2dita.ini</filepath> file.
Review the TopicHeadings documentation in <xref href = "thefm2ditainifile.xml#id131KAB00P5Z"
type = "topic" format = "dita" scope = "local"></xref>.</p>
<p>This command is useful for estimating the number of topics in
a book based on the specification of different heading levels.</p></body></topic>
